{"type": "article", "id": 3349, "title": "M1金属家具系列", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-07T07:56:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232642t41GcH2DL7ZEWXNK.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t瑞士设计工作室 Kind of Design 推出了他们的全新家具系列作品「M1」，包括一张支撑部位可用于置物架功能的桌子、一款小型边桌（亦可作为矮凳）、一把椅子、一盏台灯以及一个果篮。这是设计团队首次尝试用金属材质制作家具，全部生产皆是在瑞士完成。M1 系列的特点在于其棱角分明的几何造型，并搭配以大胆明亮的用色。定价 399－899 瑞士法郎不等，<a href=\"http://www.kindofdesign.ch/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232639puANmGOYLdjnwq9a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6921875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232639OsThnziAupYW3VGw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4453125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232640R5FP0tXqW2NdyVUc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4453125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232640GNAnXaPRVjEDbfMB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4453125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232641kSzYxPKr1FZR2UIM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4453125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}